# MQL5 Trading Project

This is an MQL5 trading project containing Expert Advisors (EAs) for MetaTrader 5 platform.

## Project Structure
- **MQL5/**: Contains MetaTrader 5 Expert Advisors and includes  
- Main project: Position Sizer EA for calculating trading position sizes

## File Types
- `.mq5` - MQL5 source files (MetaTrader 5) 
- `.mqh` - MQL header/include files (shared between MQL4/MQL5)
- `.ex5` - Compiled MQL5 executable files

Do not modify any other file types other than `.mq5` and `.mqh`.

## Documentation
For MQL5 language reference, trading functions, and technical documentation, use: https://www.mql5.com/en/docs/trading

## Key Concepts
- **Expert Advisors (EAs)**: Automated trading programs
- **Trading Functions**: OrderSend, PositionSelect, etc. for trade management
- **Position Management**: Risk management and position sizing calculations
